bnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaOLF9N.jpg&h=96f760eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁就奇怪勒...無撚端端何妖做乜講佢...就算上晝電台節目都係講朱加成班泛民然後自己跳撚哂制<br />\n但之後朱凱廸又真係成個下晝叫人唔好搞光復元朗，又話有人唔係咁諗，唔好「中計」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LPUKWMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLPUKWMr.png&h=8134b150&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其實講得「中計」兩個字，你係當中就知咩計姐....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3a2JqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3a2JqQ.jpg&h=61347ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何妖今朝搭住朱凱廸果陣佢又好似真係無哂符咁.....<br />\n....睇返轉頭，佢真係似比何妖揸住D野咁...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:02:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔夠你鬼 大家直接block 已check</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1428ca13e2bb0b3e9dda4a9b17c0a92dc78aa406","tid":1357631,"uid":282325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:03:26.000Z","msg":"負評上一頁由佢沉"},{"pid":"b226ae55d46d36c700356d02fd8a2d02b18121fc","tid":1357631,"uid":217553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:03:57.000Z","msg":"我朋友著白衫....我今日同佢傾計.....佢同我講....何妖有連登ac.....仲話佢係p牌仔....最令我目定口呆既係....佢ac叫虛偽君子.....我真係呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2491674af77c1828205ab201f392104359c104b0","tid":1357631,"uid":242238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:05:28.000Z","msg":"五毛滾返大陸"},{"pid":"e6004a06407d10ee856f0dd8844f4570b9eb9d87","tid":1357631,"uid":168818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:06:38.000Z","msg":"Bye p牌仔 俾人block哂喇 <br />\n開個新acc再帶風向啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}